in the water coarse to protect the cryptobiotic soil<\/b>.\n<\/p>\n<meta property=\"mw:PageProp\/toc\" \/>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Approach\">Approach<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>There are many routes that you can take to reach the top.  The main route extends the hike.  The alternate route will require a climb through the cliff band.\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Descent\">Descent<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>All three rappels are impressive and worthwhile.<br \/>\n<b>Rap 1<\/b> 170ft off tree CDL: 37.09351, -112.53635  Rap is set to avoid dropping in on the Arch site. <br \/>\nAfter dropping into Rap 1.  Ascend CDR approx. 80' to the archeological  site.  Please do not trample and respect the site.\n<br \/>\nContinue down canyon and stay in the watercourse to protect the soil.<br \/>\n<b>Rap 2<\/b> 180ft off tree: 37.09324, -112.53796  <br \/>\n<b>Rap 3<\/b> 125ft off tree: 37.09270, -112.53920\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Exit\">Exit<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>continue down canyon to road back to car.\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Red_tape\">Red tape<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Beta_sites\">Beta sites<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Trip_reports_and_media\">Trip reports and media<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Background\">Background<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>First documented descent by Ron Lebfrom Solo in November 2017.  Although the area was inhabited by the Paiute, the canyon was named in the language of the Navajo. Nizhoni is the Navajo word for \"beautiful.\"\nFound evidence of webbing on the last rappel.  Local rock climbers have descended the last rappel.\nFilmed in 2017, I had obtained approval from both the airport manager and the BLM Kanab field office to fly the drone before the current regulations were in place. However, flying drones in this area is now prohibited.\n<\/p><p>{{#ev:vimeo|240385300}}\n<\/p><p>Rap 1 FD: First descent solo flying drone while rappelling in 2017 before all the drone regulations were implemented.<br \/> (Checked in with the Kanab airport before flying at that time.  The airport manager expressed gratitude for the check-in.):\n{{#ev:vimeo|244148540}}<br \/>\n<\/p><p><br \/>\nRare drone footage of rap 2 and rap 1:\n<\/p><p>{{#ev:vimeo|988038174}}<br \/>\n<\/p><p>The arch site was unknown to BLM at the time in 2017.  The documented vandalism was presented to the BLM and law enforcement.\n{{#ev:vimeo|244152350}}\n<\/p><p><br \/>\nThe Coral pink sand dunes is a worthwhile destination when you are in the area.\n{{#ev:vimeo|245134757}}<br \/>\n<\/p><p><b>In Memory of Luca Chiarabini<\/b><br \/>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/235242803\">https:\/\/vimeo.com\/235242803<\/a>  <br \/>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https:\/\/lucamemorial.org\/\">https:\/\/lucamemorial.org\/<\/a>\n<\/p>\n\n\n<\/div>","technicalRating":3,"waterRating":"A","rappelLongestMeters":54.86,"vehicle":"Passenger","rappelCountMin":3,"shuttleSeconds":null,"version":"13dde3c9b0e1292371fc77483c3dc15b4d4f54a84f40d2db61d966c49bd64a25"}